ions age  further readingedit p birks ‘the content of fiduciary obligation’   israel law journal    trust law international  m conaglen ‘the nature and function of fiduciary loyalty’   law quarterly review    jh langbein ‘questioning the trust law duty of loyalty’   yale law journal    a hicks ‘the trustee act  and the modern meaning of investment’    trust law international  da de mott beyond metaphor an analysis of fiduciary obligation   duke law journal  pd finn the fiduciary principle in tg youdan ed equity fiduciaries and trusts  carswell t frankel fiduciary law  california law review  dr paling ‘trustees duties of skill and care’   conveyancer    ej weinrib ‘the fiduciary obligation’   university of toronto law journal    li rotman fiduciary laws holy grail reconciling theory and practice in fiduciary jurisprudence   boston university law review  li rotman fiduciary doctrine a concept in need of understanding   alberta law review  bryan mw and vj vann equity  trusts in australia cambridge university press nd ed ch  the following books cover the field in detail chodos rafael the law of fiduciary duties  blackthorne legal press finn pd fiduciary obligations  the law book co frankel tamar fiduciary law  fathom publishing company frankel tamar legal duries of fiduciaries  fathom publishing company frankel tamar fiduciary law  oxford university press isbn  rotman leonard i fiduciary law  thomsoncarswell isbn  external linksedit fiduciary and nonfiduciary responsibilities dictionarycomword of the day archivefiduciary fiduciary  f duty defined  explained the lectric law library  legal resources and definitions fiduciary law  legal definition legal definitions legal terms dictionary lawcom law dictionary fiduciary iman anabtawi and lynn a stout fiduciary duties for activist shareholders ucla school of law lawecon research paper no  social science research network ssrn electronic library meeting your fiduciary responsibilities the us department of labor employee benefi